17:48.701 --> 17:51.569
What was the fight about?

17:51.604 --> 17:54.338
His affair.

17:55.773 --> 17:59.109
Your father told you he was
having an affair before he died?

17:59.143 --> 18:02.279
He didn't tell me.

18:02.313 --> 18:04.514
I found a letter.

18:06.751 --> 18:09.052
(Paper rustles)

18:09.086 --> 18:11.254
Do you want to read it?

18:17.160 --> 18:19.428
Would you like me to read it?

18:21.831 --> 18:23.799
It's nothing terribly creative.

18:23.833 --> 18:29.137
Just a declaration of her love.

18:29.171 --> 18:31.740
But I need to talk to this woman.

18:31.774 --> 18:33.241
Why?

18:33.276 --> 18:37.479
Even if you knew who she
was, how would that help you?

18:37.513 --> 18:39.046
What would you say to her?

18:39.081 --> 18:43.016
My mother said my father
was alone when he died.

18:44.419 --> 18:47.187
But maybe he wasn't.

18:47.221 --> 18:49.523
Maybe... 

18:49.557 --> 18:53.059
he was with her,

18:53.094 --> 18:55.629
and if she was, then... 

18:55.664 --> 18:58.230
maybe she could tell me... 

18:59.866 --> 19:02.802
just... I need to know my
dad didn't die hating me.

19:02.836 --> 19:05.571
Sam.

19:08.776 --> 19:11.411
(Crying)

19:12.479 --> 19:14.045
(Sniffles)

19:17.383 --> 19:20.319
