19:27.327 --> 19:29.593
Well, then he's unable to
pay his employee's salaries.

19:29.628 --> 19:31.829
Yes, that's the argument
you put before the judge.

19:31.863 --> 19:33.096
He didn't like it then.

19:33.131 --> 19:36.334
