19:49.547 --> 19:51.148
Um, if I were you, I would consider

19:51.182 --> 19:53.016
that what's in the best
interest of my client

19:53.051 --> 19:55.552
is also in the best
interest of your client.

19:55.586 --> 19:58.956
If he defaults on his obligation... 

19:58.990 --> 20:01.024
There you go.

20:01.059 --> 20:03.492
You're welcome.

20:03.526 --> 20:05.895
Richard?

20:05.929 --> 20:06.963
(Chuckles) Hi.

20:06.997 --> 20:08.097
Hi.

20:09.699 --> 20:11.600
