20:11.634 --> 20:13.502
You work at this store?

20:13.536 --> 20:15.804
Oh. No, I own this store.

20:15.839 --> 20:17.306
No. No, I knew that.

20:17.341 --> 20:18.473
I just didn't want you to
think I was stalking you.

20:18.507 --> 20:19.741
You're stalking me?

20:19.775 --> 20:21.877
No. No. No. Um, this is going very bad.

20:21.911 --> 20:23.278
Very bad. (Clears throat)

20:23.312 --> 20:26.381
Hi. I heard that you owned this place,

20:26.415 --> 20:28.583
and I thought, hey, I just
got this new apartment,

20:28.617 --> 20:29.985
and I have very bad taste.

20:30.019 --> 20:31.086
It's a furnished apartment,

20:31.120 --> 20:32.754
and that's probably my first mistake.

20:32.788 --> 20:34.855
Mm. Well, it depends on who furnished it.

20:34.890 --> 20:36.823
Maybe Richard Grieco.

20:36.858 --> 20:38.192
Oh. (Laughs)

20:38.226 --> 20:40.694
Thank you for laughing.

20:40.728 --> 20:42.997
Yeah, I... I think I can help you.

20:43.031 --> 20:46.300
Maybe we can start with some
throw pillows and go from there.

20:46.334 --> 20:47.501
- Throw pillows?
- Yeah.

20:47.535 --> 20:50.169
Excellent. Would you have
dinner with me tonight?

20:50.204 --> 20:51.504
Tonight?

20:51.538 --> 20:52.705
I'll still buy the throw
pillows if you say no.

20:52.739 --> 20:54.540
I just had to ask you.

20:54.574 --> 20:57.243
I think I can get a sitter by 6:00.

20:57.278 --> 20:58.278
Great. (Laughs)

20:58.312 --> 21:00.613
Yeah. Um... 

21:00.647 --> 21:03.216
- Would you like to show me the, um...
- Yeah, some throw pillows.

21:03.250 --> 21:05.318
Right. Right. The throw pillows.

21:08.254 --> 21:09.487
(Telephone rings in distance)

21:09.522 --> 21:10.956
So I guess you got plans tonight,

21:10.990 --> 21:13.191
given your, uh, attire.

21:13.226 --> 21:14.960
Not at this rate.

21:14.994 --> 21:17.495
Okay,

21:17.530 --> 21:20.732
I will have your work done
and on your desk by 8:00 A.M.

21:20.766 --> 21:23.234
If you let me take a
look at you in that thing.

21:24.669 --> 21:25.903
That's quite an offer.

21:25.938 --> 21:29.307
No work in mind for a mere ten seconds.

21:29.341 --> 21:31.242
(Ring)

21:31.276 --> 21:32.343
(Ring)

21:37.349 --> 21:38.581
Five seconds.

21:42.820 --> 21:44.321
Done.

21:57.434 --> 21:58.968
One,

21:59.002 --> 22:00.102
two,

22:00.136 --> 22:01.937
three,

22:01.972 --> 22:03.538
four,

22:03.573 --> 22:04.673
five.

22:27.887 --> 22:30.755
Ooh. Wow. The place looks great.

22:30.789 --> 22:31.955
Do you have a reservation?

22:31.990 --> 22:34.292
You never remember me.

22:34.326 --> 22:37.127
It's amazing.

22:37.162 --> 22:39.029
I'm Savi, Harry's wife.

22:39.063 --> 22:40.964
Oh. Right.

22:40.999 --> 22:42.933
I'll, uh, let him know you're here.

22:42.967 --> 22:45.201
♪

22:45.235 --> 22:46.202
Actually, I got it.

22:46.236 --> 22:49.706
♪

22:49.740 --> 22:51.274
Hey, baby.

22:51.309 --> 22:52.975
Mmm.

22:53.010 --> 22:55.244
Nice to see you, too.

22:55.279 --> 22:56.746
Didn't know you were coming.

22:56.781 --> 22:58.415
Yeah, I wanted to see you,

22:58.449 --> 23:02.618
