23:20.669 --> 23:23.671
I'm just... trying to have some fun.

23:23.706 --> 23:25.540
And what about this is fun for me?

23:25.574 --> 23:27.875
I've spent the entire day trying
to forget about this morning.

23:29.244 --> 23:31.245
Oh, my God.

23:32.848 --> 23:35.483
