23:35.517 --> 23:37.184
- I was just trying...
- Trying to what?

23:38.720 --> 23:40.053
Can I please get back to work now?

23:40.087 --> 23:41.688
Yeah.

23:48.463 --> 23:51.531
Actually, this is a fabulous craftsman.

23:51.566 --> 23:54.367
