you around the earth on this.

23:57.704 --> 23:58.838
- Sorry.
- No.

23:58.872 --> 24:00.473
Well, for the money I'm willing to spend,

24:00.507 --> 24:01.741
I want it to be perfect.

24:01.775 --> 24:03.476
Naturally.

24:03.510 --> 24:05.411
And I... but I do like this one.

24:05.445 --> 24:06.645
