24:51.087 --> 24:53.322
My poor angel.

24:53.356 --> 24:55.625
He needs closure, Elizabeth.

24:55.659 --> 24:57.460
(Sighs deeply)

24:57.494 --> 24:59.127
He especially fixated on the fact

24:59.161 --> 25:00.995
that Thomas was alone when he died.

25:01.030 --> 25:02.964
I never should have told him that.

25:02.998 --> 25:04.933
No, it's best Sam knows the truth.

25:06.235 --> 25:08.069
But it's not the truth.

25:08.103 --> 25:10.472
He wasn't alone.

25:10.506 --> 25:12.607
I was with him.

25:12.642 --> 25:15.075
But I thought... 

25:16.311 --> 25:17.645
