25:17.679 --> 25:19.279
That he did it to himself?

25:21.550 --> 25:26.219
When the time came, he asked for my help,

25:26.254 --> 25:28.288
and I gave it to him.

25:28.323 --> 25:31.290
Thomas said that's why you
gave him the prescription,

25:31.325 --> 25:33.893
for when things got too painful... 

25:35.262 --> 25:36.629
and they did.

25:36.664 --> 25:40.399
(Crying) I know I never
should've lied to Sam,

25:40.434 --> 25:43.102
but he would never understand the truth,

25:43.136 --> 25:44.604
and I know he'd never forgive me

25:44.638 --> 25:48.173
for taking away his
chance to say good-bye.

25:48.207 --> 25:49.374
(Sniffles)

25:49.408 --> 25:51.109
You did the right thing

25:51.143 --> 25:54.212
for Sam... 

25:54.246 --> 25:56.114
and for Thomas.

25:57.684 --> 25:59.451
I should go.

26:00.487 --> 26:02.920
(Sniffles)

26:02.955 --> 26:05.422
Thank you, Karen.

26:05.457 --> 26:07.859
You've done so much for us.

