29:02.872 --> 29:04.906
You could've told us the truth.

29:04.941 --> 29:08.143
You would've told me to stop seeing him.

29:08.177 --> 29:09.644
I wouldn't have told you that.

29:09.678 --> 29:11.646
(Laughs)

29:11.680 --> 29:14.516
I've always known that there was

29:14.550 --> 29:16.784
something between Tom
and me for a long time,

29:16.818 --> 29:20.821
but when he told me he was sick... 

29:20.856 --> 29:22.957
(Voice breaks) I just
wanted to be with him.

29:26.161 --> 29:30.230
And I convinced myself that it was okay,

29:30.265 --> 29:32.299
that we were soul mates.

29:32.333 --> 29:34.000
Maybe you were.

29:34.035 --> 29:36.069
(Crying) No, because in
the end, he chose his wife.

29:36.103 --> 29:39.606
That's who he wanted to be
with in his last moments,

29:39.641 --> 29:42.208
which means the whole time, I was just... 

29:43.743 --> 29:45.545
a mistress.

29:45.579 --> 29:47.713
(Scoffs)

29:47.747 --> 29:50.049
I'm so sorry, honey.

29:50.083 --> 29:52.117
It's the worst feeling in the world,

29:52.152 --> 29:53.952
losing the person you love.

29:53.987 --> 29:57.589
(Josslyn) No offense, but
I feel worse for his kid.

29:57.623 --> 29:59.157
Sounds like he's a mess, you know?

29:59.192 --> 30:01.193
I know.

30:01.227 --> 30:03.295
I feel like I owe it to Sam to help him.

30:03.329 --> 30:04.829
I just don't know how.

30:06.131 --> 30:07.932
You have to cut ties with the son

30:07.966 --> 30:09.501
and the wife.

30:09.535 --> 30:10.602
What?

30:10.636 --> 30:12.836
I can't just abandon them.

30:12.870 --> 30:15.906
Karen, this is a malpractice
suit waiting to happen.

30:15.940 --> 30:18.609
If anyone finds out that you
were sleeping with your patient,

30:18.643 --> 30:23.013
let alone prescribing him
lethal doses of morphine,

30:23.047 --> 30:25.415
Karen, you could lose your license.

30:25.449 --> 30:29.285
I know, but Sam's in
pain, and he's Tom's son.

30:29.320 --> 30:31.755
Yeah, but he's not your son,

30:31.789 --> 30:34.457
and you're not Tom's wife.

30:38.995 --> 30:40.295
(Telephone rings)

30:40.330 --> 30:42.865
Are you being stalked, Savannah?

30:42.899 --> 30:43.966
What?

30:44.000 --> 30:45.768
Rick Anderson left this.

30:45.802 --> 30:47.569
Says he's been tracking
some numbers for you.

30:47.604 --> 30:49.271
Have you been getting obscene phone calls?

30:49.305 --> 30:50.372
It's for a friend.

30:50.406 --> 30:53.908
Oh. You want some obscene phone calls?

30:53.943 --> 30:56.410
I can do that.

30:56.445 --> 30:58.246
April, it's Savi.

30:58.280 --> 31:00.581
Listen, call me as soon as
you get this message, okay?

31:00.616 --> 31:01.883
Is this what you do all day,

31:01.917 --> 31:03.084
talk to your friends on the phone?

31:03.119 --> 31:04.085
Told you I could've been a lawyer.

31:04.120 --> 31:05.286
What are you doing here?

31:05.320 --> 31:06.420
I need a favor.

31:06.455 --> 31:09.189
My landlord officially kicked me out.

31:09.224 --> 31:11.091
Mm, so are you moving into Mac's house?

31:11.126 --> 31:12.492
Yeah. No, that's not gonna work out.

31:12.526 --> 31:14.327
Because you realized he
was sequestering you away

31:14.362 --> 31:16.230
just to have sex with you
whenever it pleased him?

31:16.264 --> 31:18.431
Yes, Savi. Okay? You were right,

31:18.466 --> 31:20.801
and that's why I thought we
should spend more time together,

31:20.835 --> 31:22.269
so that I can learn

31:22.303 --> 31:23.870
these valuable life
lessons from my big sister.

31:23.904 --> 31:25.604
What is it? What do you need?

31:25.639 --> 31:27.006
You always said I could
move into the pool house

31:27.040 --> 31:29.308
if need arose.

31:29.342 --> 31:30.442
It's arisen.

31:32.379 --> 31:33.412
Hmm.

31:33.446 --> 31:34.480
Please.

31:34.514 --> 31:35.714
Fine.

31:35.749 --> 31:37.150
- Really?
- Yes.

31:37.184 --> 31:38.284
Oh, thank you. Thank you.
Thank you. Thank you. Thank you.

31:38.318 --> 31:40.786
Hello. What is happening over there?

31:44.123 --> 31:45.190
Ooh.

31:45.224 --> 31:46.357
Not for you.

31:46.392 --> 31:48.260
Oh. Mmm.

31:48.294 --> 31:51.429
I can't believe it's come to this.

31:51.463 --> 31:53.198
Come to what?

31:53.232 --> 31:57.734
Aren't we doing freudian thing
where you whip out a ball,

31:57.769 --> 32:00.037
ask me to play catch,
repair my inner child?

32:00.071 --> 32:01.705
(Laughs) No.

32:01.739 --> 32:02.840
Good.

32:02.874 --> 32:05.176
'Cause I throw like a girl.

32:05.210 --> 32:09.079
It's impossible to imagine what
goes through a person's mind

32:09.114 --> 32:11.348
when they know they're about to die.

32:11.382 --> 32:13.549
With your dad, all he wanted was

32:13.583 --> 32:17.053
to revisit the happiest
moments of his life.

32:18.889 --> 32:20.890
He coached your little league here?

32:20.925 --> 32:22.692
He did.

32:22.726 --> 32:26.229
You made a double play right there

32:26.263 --> 32:30.632
to clinch your championship that year.

32:30.666 --> 32:33.168
And that was one of his happiest moments?

32:33.203 --> 32:37.405
Not because you won,
but because when you won,

32:37.440 --> 32:42.377
all the players on your team
rushed each other to celebrate,

32:42.411 --> 32:45.713
but you rushed to your dad.

32:45.747 --> 32:47.815
I remember.

32:49.718 --> 32:51.953
His last few weeks,

32:51.987 --> 32:55.156
he came here every day.

32:55.190 --> 32:58.759
So I think... 

32:58.793 --> 33:00.393
whatever you said to him,

33:00.427 --> 33:02.062
whatever you regret,

33:02.096 --> 33:08.501
it didn't take away from
the love he had for you.

33:08.535 --> 33:10.170
Was it you?

33:12.139 --> 33:14.374
Were you the one he was sleeping with?

33:15.776 --> 33:19.211
No, Sam, I wasn't.

33:20.947 --> 33:24.716
It's time to move on.

33:29.422 --> 33:31.623
Thank you.

33:31.657 --> 33:33.791
Thank you so much.

33:35.094 --> 33:38.029
Are you sure this is
where the calls came from?

33:38.063 --> 33:40.365
Well, the last one at least.

33:42.768 --> 33:44.135
Okay.

33:44.169 --> 33:45.803
Here it is.

33:49.507 --> 33:50.974
(Sighs)

33:54.712 --> 33:56.280
Yes? Can I help you?

33:56.314 --> 33:58.681
Hi. Um, I'm April Malloy,

33:58.716 --> 34:01.251
and I've been receiving phone calls... 

34:01.286 --> 34:02.552
prank calls, I guess... 

34:02.586 --> 34:05.487
and they were traced to this room, so... 

34:05.522 --> 34:06.722
That's weird.

34:06.756 --> 34:08.257
How long have you been here?

34:08.292 --> 34:10.059
Uh, we checked in two days ago.

34:10.092 --> 34:11.060
We?

34:11.094 --> 34:13.429
My son and me.

34:13.463 --> 34:14.797
You know what? (Chuckles)

34:14.831 --> 34:17.433
He has this obsession with phones.

34:17.467 --> 34:19.135
Maybe that's what happened.

34:19.168 --> 34:20.768
So sorry. Scottie, sweetie,

34:20.803 --> 34:22.870
come here and apologize to this nice woman.

34:22.905 --> 34:24.806
Oh, no, no, no. That's fine.

34:24.840 --> 34:26.107
Thank you. Thank you for your time.

34:26.141 --> 34:27.775
Thank you.

34:27.810 --> 34:29.143
(Door closes)

34:32.081 --> 34:35.516
You okay?

34:35.551 --> 34:37.284
Oh, I feel so stupid.

34:37.319 --> 34:41.455
No. No, honey, don't feel
stupid. It's not stupid.

34:41.489 --> 34:44.123
He was the best man I ever knew.

34:47.195 --> 34:49.362
But I have to let go.

34:50.364 --> 34:52.630
I'm ready.

34:52.666 --> 34:55.001
I really think I'm ready now.

34:55.034 --> 34:57.170
I know you are.

34:57.204 --> 34:59.138
(Crying) Thank you.

34:59.173 --> 35:00.573
It's okay.

35:03.210 --> 35:04.777
Let's go.

35:11.551 --> 35:13.652
(Josslyn) This is gonna take
me five minutes to clean up.

35:13.687 --> 35:15.287
I promise.

35:21.962 --> 35:23.395
You're late for work, aren't you?

35:23.429 --> 35:26.063
Running out now.

35:31.971 --> 35:33.705
By the way, Joss is only staying here

35:33.739 --> 35:36.040
until she finds a place.

35:39.011 --> 35:41.879
Sorry I didn't ask you first.

35:41.913 --> 35:43.847
It's fine.

35:43.882 --> 35:47.384
A little passive-aggressive
on your part, but whatever.

35:48.586 --> 35:50.954
(Sighs)

35:50.989 --> 35:52.890
Is that how we're doing it now?

35:52.924 --> 35:54.190
Doing what?

35:54.225 --> 35:56.359
Talk to me, Harry.

35:56.394 --> 35:58.228
What do you want to talk about?

35:58.262 --> 36:00.930
I don't care. Anything.
Just if we keep going at it

36:00.964 --> 36:02.332
like this, it's only gonna get worse.

36:02.366 --> 36:03.400
How much worse can it get?

36:03.434 --> 36:05.101
I mean, you showing up last night

36:05.136 --> 36:06.369
in that desperate getup was

36:06.404 --> 36:07.504
an all-time lie, don't you think?

36:07.538 --> 36:08.505
I was trying to connect with you.

36:08.539 --> 36:10.006
Right. Okay, because honestly,

36:10.041 --> 36:12.375
that's something I haven't
felt in a long time.

36:12.410 --> 36:13.742
Right. And that's my fault, is it?

36:13.776 --> 36:15.344
No, I'm not saying it's your fault.

36:15.378 --> 36:17.446
I'm just... 

36:17.480 --> 36:20.449
I'm trying to figure out what comes next.

36:20.483 --> 36:22.384
What comes next? Okay. Well, that's easy.

36:22.419 --> 36:24.786
We can, uh, stop counting days

36:24.820 --> 36:26.321
and we can stop taking your temperature

36:26.356 --> 36:27.523
and doing all that other crap,

36:27.557 --> 36:29.090
and you can stop worrying
that having a baby

36:29.124 --> 36:31.092
is gonna prevent you from making partner.

36:31.126 --> 36:32.427
That's not fair.

36:32.461 --> 36:33.794
But it's true, though,
right? I mean, come on.

36:33.828 --> 36:35.396
Somewhere inside you
must be a little relieved.

36:35.431 --> 36:37.031
- Stop. Okay?
- You're the one who wanted to talk.

36:37.066 --> 36:39.700
- Stop. Stop!
- You're the one that wanted to talk!

36:45.839 --> 36:48.841
(Crying)

36:50.844 --> 36:53.746
(Sobbing)

37:04.047 --> 37:06.015
(Seagulls cry)

37:06.049 --> 37:10.285
♪

37:10.319 --> 37:11.587
(Door closes)

37:13.356 --> 37:14.923
Oh, hi.

37:14.958 --> 37:16.124
Hi.

37:16.158 --> 37:17.793
Uh, where's Sally?

37:20.663 --> 37:22.197
Oh.

37:22.231 --> 37:23.999
She changed her mind again, didn't she?

37:24.033 --> 37:26.300
I am so sorry. She woke up this
morning, totally freaking out,

37:26.334 --> 37:27.902
because now she doesn't
want to live near the water.

37:27.936 --> 37:29.537
It was a whole... 

37:29.571 --> 37:31.338
It's okay. We'll keep looking.
Alex, it's totally fine.

37:31.373 --> 37:34.375
Uh, really, I would understand
it if you want to drop

37:34.409 --> 37:37.077
us neurotic lesbians.

37:37.112 --> 37:39.346
It's a lot to deal with.
Probably not your thing.

37:39.381 --> 37:41.681
I wouldn't exactly say that.

37:41.716 --> 37:43.750
Besides, you know what?
I love a proper challenge.

37:43.784 --> 37:45.552
So... 

37:45.586 --> 37:46.720
Oh.

37:46.754 --> 37:48.054
Why not?

37:48.088 --> 37:50.490
♪

37:50.525 --> 37:52.325
(Exhales deeply)

37:53.661 --> 37:56.529
Well, for what it's worth,

37:56.563 --> 38:00.666
I could totally see myself living here.

38:00.700 --> 38:02.801
Yeah, me, too.

38:02.836 --> 38:05.470
♪

38:05.505 --> 38:07.072
(Door bells jingle)

38:07.106 --> 38:09.074
I was halfway to your house when you called

38:09.108 --> 38:10.643
and canceled on me last night.

38:10.677 --> 38:12.244
Oh, no. I'm sorry.

38:12.278 --> 38:14.512
You should be. I bought a
new shirt and everything.

38:14.547 --> 38:16.480
- You did?
- No.

38:16.515 --> 38:19.350
♪

38:22.688 --> 38:24.088
Look, I just want you to know

38:24.122 --> 38:26.925
that that was a onetime freak-out.

38:26.959 --> 38:28.592
I promise it wouldn't happen again

38:28.626 --> 38:31.995
if you ever ask me out again,
which you probably wouldn't.

38:32.030 --> 38:34.064
<i>Well, you could always ask me out.</i>

38:34.098 --> 38:36.667
That's true. I could.

38:36.701 --> 38:39.502
I never thought about that.

38:39.537 --> 38:43.040
Richard, would you like to go
out to dinner with me sometime?

38:43.074 --> 38:44.541
How about tonight?

38:44.575 --> 38:47.076
Tonight?

38:47.110 --> 38:49.545
I don't know I if could get a sitter,

38:49.580 --> 38:51.413
and... and this morning,
it looked like Lucy was

38:51.448 --> 38:53.282
about to get pinkeye.

38:53.316 --> 38:55.350
<i>*</i>

38:55.385 --> 38:57.587
Tonight sounds perfect.

38:57.621 --> 38:59.288
Pick me up at 8:00.

38:59.322 --> 39:00.422
Okay.

39:00.457 --> 39:01.790
You don't know where I live.

39:01.824 --> 39:03.792
(Laughs)

39:03.826 --> 39:05.727
No. Good morning, gorgeous.

39:05.761 --> 39:08.529
Not today, Dom. Sorry.

39:08.564 --> 39:10.264
Isn't that Thomas Grey's wife?

39:10.299 --> 39:12.200
- Mm-hmm.
- What is she doing here?

39:12.234 --> 39:13.702
Michael's been with her all morning.

39:13.736 --> 39:16.004
Apparently, since she denied the autopsy,

39:16.038 --> 39:18.005
insurance is trying to deny the claim.

39:18.039 --> 39:19.873
The firm's getting into it.

39:19.908 --> 39:21.809
Doctor, Sam Grey is here to see you.

39:21.843 --> 39:23.110
Did he make an appointment?

39:23.144 --> 39:25.312
No.

39:25.346 --> 39:26.446
Sam, come in.

39:27.482 --> 39:29.149
What are you doing here?

39:29.183 --> 39:32.086
These are for you, to
thank you for everything.

39:34.421 --> 39:36.122
But mostly I just wanted
an excuse to see you again.

39:36.156 --> 39:37.924
Sam, I can't see you,

39:37.958 --> 39:40.559
but, uh, I can recommend
you to another doctor.

39:40.594 --> 39:42.361
I'm not here to see you as a patient.

39:45.365 --> 39:48.067
Oh, no.

39:48.102 --> 39:49.335
Sam... 

39:49.369 --> 39:51.737
I want to take you for
coffee if you have time.

39:51.771 --> 39:55.774
- You have to go. I have a patient now.
- (Cell phone rings)

39:55.808 --> 39:57.610
I'll call you.

39:57.644 --> 40:00.846
(Ring)

40:00.880 --> 40:02.047
Oh.

40:03.950 --> 40:05.283
Hey, Savi.

40:05.317 --> 40:07.985
Hey. I only have a minute, okay,

40:08.020 --> 40:10.155
but there's some question
about Thomas' death.

40:10.189 --> 40:12.423
Yeah, the insurance company
is launching an investigation

40:12.458 --> 40:14.125
that my firm is handling.

40:14.160 --> 40:15.693
Now it's probably just a routine thing,

40:15.727 --> 40:17.362
but I thought you should be aware.

40:17.396 --> 40:20.031
Stay away from that family.

40:20.065 --> 40:22.332
I will. Yes.

40:22.367 --> 40:23.967
Thanks, Savi.

40:25.403 --> 40:27.471
(Beep)

40:31.543 --> 40:32.976
Oh.

40:33.010 --> 40:36.280
(Chuckles) I'm sorry.
What are you doing here?

40:36.314 --> 40:38.782
How did you... 

40:38.816 --> 40:41.551
I wasn't expecting you yesterday. I... 

40:41.585 --> 40:43.953
I've been trying to work
up the nerve for weeks

40:43.988 --> 40:46.222
to actually talk to you when I called.

40:46.256 --> 40:47.423
Who are you?

40:47.457 --> 40:48.658
My name is Miranda.

40:48.693 --> 40:49.993
I knew your husband.

40:51.395 --> 40:53.129
We were in love.

40:53.164 --> 40:54.629
I'm sorry. You have to get out of here.

40:54.664 --> 40:55.864
You have to get out of here right now.

40:55.899 --> 40:58.033
And I was pregnant when he died.

41:20.756 --> 41:23.758
(Siren wailing in distance)

41:28.796 --> 41:31.231
I thought you left.

41:31.265 --> 41:34.167
No. I wanted to get a jump on this work.

41:34.202 --> 41:35.401
You okay?

41:35.436 --> 41:39.039
You need some help?

41:39.073 --> 41:40.774
No, it's okay.

41:40.808 --> 41:43.308
You sure? I can stay if you want.

41:46.479 --> 41:48.347
No. I'm fine.

41:48.381 --> 41:50.850
- (Sets folder down)
- I should go.

41:52.152 --> 41:53.819
I'm fine.

41:53.854 --> 41:55.687
You don't seem fine.

41:57.757 --> 42:00.725
It's okay to let go, Savannah. You don't... 

42:00.760 --> 42:02.227
you don't have to be strong for me.

42:05.898 --> 42:07.899
(Alex Clare's "Damn your eyes" playing)

42:11.237 --> 42:13.204
♪ I can do what I want ♪

42:13.239 --> 42:15.806
♪ I'm in complete control ♪

42:15.840 --> 42:18.341
♪ that's what I tell myself ♪

42:18.376 --> 42:19.943
♪ I got a mind of my own ♪

42:19.978 --> 42:22.712
♪ I'll be all right alone ♪

42:22.747 --> 42:26.150
♪ don't need anybody else ♪

42:26.184 --> 42:29.486
♪ I gave myself a good talking-to ♪

42:29.520 --> 42:32.421
♪ no more being a fool for you ♪

42:33.957 --> 42:36.392
♪ I remember ♪

42:36.426 --> 42:38.928
♪ how you make me want to surrender ♪

